org.matrix.androidsdk.data.store

Interface IMXStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MXFileStore, MXMemoryStore

    public interface IMXStore
    An interface for storing and retrieving Matrix objects.

      • commit

        void commit()
        Save changes in the store. If the store uses permanent storage like database or file, it is the optimised time to commit the last changes.

      • open

      • getEventReceipts

        java.util.List<ReceiptData> getEventReceipts(java.lang.String roomId,
                                             java.lang.String eventId,
                                             boolean excludeSelf,
                                             boolean sort)
        Returns the receipts list for an event in a dedicated room. if sort is set to YES, they are sorted from the latest to the oldest ones.
        Parameters:
        roomId - The room Id.
        eventId - The event Id. (null to retrieve all existing receipts)
        excludeSelf - exclude the oneself read receipts.
        sort - to sort them from the latest to the oldest
        Returns:
        the receipts for an event in a dedicated room.
